-- Root cause: seed.sql is LOCAL-ONLY (supabase db reset / supabase start).
-- Migration 20260615000001_real_plz_data.sql references Sozialamt Berlin
-- (UUID 10000000-...-000001) which did not exist in any migration → FK
-- violation → that entire migration rolled back → postal_code_rule and
-- social_office are empty in production.
--
-- This migration (dated 20260614) runs BEFORE 20260615, so it inserts
-- Sozialamt Berlin first, unblocking the PLZ migration on re-run / push.
--
-- All inserts use ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING so re-running is safe.
-- Split: part 1 of 2 — social_office → question
-- ============================================================

